ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, &ouml;&#328;ki
g&ouml;wrelilikler barada hronologiki tertipde, hakyky g&ouml;wreliligi&#328;
n&auml;medigi, &ouml;&#328;ki g&ouml;wreliligi&#328; gidi&#351;i barada
(toksikoz, gestoz, &yacute;&uuml;rek-damar ulgamyny&#328; keselleri,
b&ouml;wrekler, bagyr we be&yacute;leki organlar), olary&#328;
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary we jikme-jik maglumatlary &yacute;ygnal&yacute;ar.
Netije.&nbsp;&Ouml;&#328;ki ginekologiki keselleri&#328;, dowamly keselleri&#328;,
agyr nesil yzarlamasyny&#328;, in&ccedil;ekeseli&#328;, sifilisi&#328;, akyl,
onkologiki keselleri&#328;, erbet endikleri&#328; (&ccedil;ilim &ccedil;ekmek,
alkogol, ne&#351;e seri&#351;deleri) bardygyny
a&yacute;dy&#328;la&#351;dyr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Lukman a&yacute;aly&#328;
bedenini&#328; k&ouml;p&ccedil;&uuml;lik g&ouml;rkezijisini
kesgitle&yacute;&auml;r, agramy&#328; dinamikasyny kesgitle&yacute;&auml;r, gan
basy&#351;yny we &yacute;&uuml;rek urmasyny
&ouml;l&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&Ccedil;anaklary&#328; ululygyny
&ouml;l&ccedil;emek, s&uuml;&yacute;demdiriji m&auml;zleri&#328; ulalmagyna,
olary&#328; dartylmagyna baha bermek, s&uuml;&yacute;demdiriji m&auml;zlere
basylanda (ilkinji g&ouml;wreli a&yacute;allarda) emzikde a&ccedil;yl&yacute;an
s&uuml;&yacute;t kanallaryndan i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; d&ouml;remegini&#328;
barlygyny barlamak &uuml;&ccedil;in ob&yacute;ektiw barlag
ge&ccedil;ir&yacute;&auml;r. .&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le hem ginekologiki
g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irili&#351;, da&#351;ky jyns agzalaryny&#328; wizual
g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irilmegi, a&yacute;nadaky waginany&#328; we
&yacute;atgyny&#328; barlagyny, &yacute;atgy we &yacute;atgy
go&#351;undylaryny&#328; ululygyny, yzygiderliligini, hereketliligini we
agyrylylygyny kesgitlemek bilen iki a&yacute;lyk waginal barlagy &ouml;z
i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar. .</span></p>

