</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Transwaginal ultrases&nbsp;(ultrases)&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>g&ouml;wrelilik
faktyny kesgitlem&auml;ge we d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328;
&ouml;s&uuml;&#351;ini&#328; irki d&ouml;w&uuml;rlerinden
&yacute;agda&yacute;yna dinamiki g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etm&auml;ge
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Eratgy arteri&yacute;alarynda, spiral arteri&yacute;alarda we
g&ouml;bek arteri&yacute;asynda &yacute;atgyny&#328; gan
a&yacute;lany&#351;yny&#328; doppler&nbsp;<b>ultrasesografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>,
&#351;e&yacute;le hem d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328; aortasyndaky we
be&yacute;nini&#328; damarlarynda d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328;
gemodinamikasy.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
