</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Pregnancyhli&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>g&ouml;wreli a&yacute;allar
&uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&uuml;rek aritmi we ge&ccedil;irijilik
n&auml;sazlyklaryny bahalandyrmak&nbsp;<b>&uuml;&ccedil;in
