<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328;&nbsp;<b>kardiotokografi&yacute;asy
(CTG), &#351;ol&nbsp;</b>d&ouml;w&uuml;rde d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328;
&yacute;&uuml;rek urmasyny hasaba almak we so&#328;raky barlag we
g&ouml;wrelilik d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde &yacute;atgyny&#328; kontraktiki
funksi&yacute;asy ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

