i&#351;lemekden we &yacute;adawlyga seb&auml;p bol&yacute;an i&#351;lerden
ga&ccedil;a durmalydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Stressli &yacute;agda&yacute;lardan we emosional tejribelerden
ga&ccedil;a durmaly.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Garyn &#351;ikeslerine, &yacute;ykylmagyna, streslere seb&auml;p
bolup biljek fiziki ma&#351;klardan ga&ccedil;a duru&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>G&ouml;wreli a&yacute;aly&#328; fiziki ta&yacute;dan
i&#351;je&#328; bolmagy, &yacute;&ouml;remegi, g&ouml;wreli a&yacute;allar
&uuml;&ccedil;in g&uuml;nde 20-30 minutlap ma&#351;k etmegi maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r (arz-&#351;ika&yacute;atlar we gar&#351;ylyklar bolmasa).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Dogry we yzygiderli i&yacute;i&#328;: g&ouml;k
&ouml;n&uuml;mleri&#328;, eti&#328;, balygy&#328;, baklaglary&#328;,
hozlary&#328;, miweleri&#328; we tutu&#351; d&auml;neleri&#328; h&ouml;kmany
suratda go&#351;ulmagy bilen belok, witaminler we minerallary&#328; i&#328;
amatly mukdary bolan &yacute;eterlik kalori&yacute;aly i&yacute;mit
i&yacute;i&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Esasanam i&ccedil;ind&auml;ki z&auml;herli bisfenol seb&auml;pli
plastmassa &ccedil;&uuml;&yacute;&#351;eleri we gap-ga&ccedil;lary ulanmakdan
ga&ccedil;a duru&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Metilmercury (tuna, akula, gyly&ccedil; balygy, maker) bilen
do&yacute;&yacute;an balyklary&#328; sarp edilmegini
&ccedil;&auml;klendiri&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A witamine ba&yacute; i&yacute;mitleri (sygyr eti, towuk
&yacute;a-da &ouml;rdek bagry) kabul etmegi&#328;izi azaldy&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Kofein kabul etmegi &ccedil;&auml;klendiri&#328; (g&uuml;nde 300
